Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...黃昏尋物.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也要麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 想挖多少就挖多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己挖的白薯自己扛 能扛動多少挖多少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 你看 連在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大個的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 就像是在尋寶似的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土 土鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩的屁股上全都是泥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?那是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比艾草保育園的小朋友們大一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這家的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 這家的孫子已經是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰家的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在附近的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我沒有及時發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 偶爾會有來胡鬧的孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在附近的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 差不多該收拾收拾回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多白薯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始應該已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己挖的自己扛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 回去烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 我一個人扛走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部扛走太勉強了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 說好了自己挖的自己扛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不行的 放棄吧 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的煙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很燙的 要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再烤一些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去分給鄰居們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君 能和小鳩一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去 那樣能快些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...但是還是一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想讓小鳩和鄰居們熟絡一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩要努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會指望你幫忙的 別礙事就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會說些別礙事之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也沒有說"別跟過來"呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他拿了我的白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想去發那些白薯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說因為好像很重 所以幫你拿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是艾草保育園的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去挖白薯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來分給您一些美味的白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是艾草保育園的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是艾草保育園的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點點 白薯就全部分完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小姑娘 好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微長大了一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 路過的 說"請借我水龍頭用用"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去挖白薯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...剛才的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了讓你站住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要說的 偷白薯賊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小偷帶到派出所去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你 都還給你還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回改成沉默不語了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他偷白薯賊就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不叫偷白薯賊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自己的名字對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君 為什麼要離家出走?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去原來的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來的家?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來住的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為媽媽換了公司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 怎麼樣了 原來的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正打算要去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想去...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址忘記了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你的表情上寫著忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘記家的地址對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 搬家的時候我還在上幼兒園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點記不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫做忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能記起是什麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許能幫你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能畫出家的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...屋頂是紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡和這裡有窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是天線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家周圍的事物也都畫下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話找起來比較容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有個郵筒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊有條狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的一條狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一經過它就會叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(吉村 啟太 TEL)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽總是為我做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我讀圖畫書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日經常帶我去野營或者遊樂園...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回到原來的家裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫啟太君尋找他的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線索只有狗和郵筒的話是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還記得什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊還是左邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就應該很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想喝嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了 必須要節約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節約?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還知道這麼難懂的詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽經常說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(請自取)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨子 看了不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換把這個留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本也有不錯的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 如果連這點都沒有的話就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給我個梨子吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...這條狗...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡...不是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能打破玻璃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要弄壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回到現在的家裡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為...有爺爺在...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和我現在住在爺爺家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君你討厭你爺爺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他很壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都大聲吵我起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 啟太 還不快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快點收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上想多看會電視 也想多玩會遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺你做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了還不快點睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯時候也總叫我吃我不喜歡吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡的東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魚啦 青菜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太 不要浪費食物 全都吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是壞心眼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 爺爺明明就是討厭我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會對我那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是想我不在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那種家...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師也經常對保育園的孩子們說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了營養均衡小魚和青菜也都要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師是很溫柔 很喜歡小孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育園的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很溫柔?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然洗好澡了就趕緊睡覺!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是不是壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想分清楚很難的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是仔細想想的話或許就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太 你是打算在這裡烤白薯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和大家一起烤過白薯 覺得很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就負起責任帶些白薯回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,農家的老婆婆那邊我會去道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙挖得太多太沉了 我也是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能一個人回去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了沒問題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊 臭老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓人擔心啊 你這笨孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽也在家等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君現在和他的爺爺準備去坐電車了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生你知道啟太君家的電話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是籐本先生把啟太君的爺爺叫來的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去蒸白薯吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是保育園的挖白薯活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要分給鄰居一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生他...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 清和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那小鬼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太君看到以前的家好像很傷心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 因為知道了爺爺的真正心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後今天因為是籐本努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以給你一半 五十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天早上的籐本先生很壞心眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那互相抵消 籐本得零分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給小鳩的努力打七十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好擦掉再重寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真多怨言啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是一半五十分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了好好擦掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 二十五分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就十二點五分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉全黑了

Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...悄悄祈禱.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:07.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:15.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:23.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:42.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:45.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:49.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:53.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:24:01.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:10.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.44,0:24:14.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:27.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議
